com.precog.client

Class AccountInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.precog.client.AccountInfo

  • public class AccountInfo
extends Object
    User account details (email, account ID, API key, root path, etc.). This holds most of the important information of a user account.
    Author:
    Gabriel Claramunt , Tom Switzer
    See Also:
    PrecogClient.createAccount(String, String), PrecogClient.createAccount(java.net.URL, String, String), PrecogClient.describeAccount(String, String, String), PrecogClient.describeAccount(java.net.URL, String, String, String)
